title: "Describing Rare Disease Trajectories: Bring Your Own Disease — GA4GH Session April 2026"
abstract: >
  Structured disease narratives, ontology mappings, and gap analyses from the
  GA4GH "Bring Your Own Disease" biohackathon session (April 16, 2026).
  Contributions are published as a FAIR Data Point and indexed in the StaticFDP ecosystem.
